{"tid":673965,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［中国已贏] 中國大削汽車及零部件進口關稅","createTime":"2018-05-22T09:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T12:47:01.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2684879714828013adcce7b35229576b8799a4c1","tid":673965,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T09:48:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180522&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58224017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180522%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58224017&d=XXRUhZubQJyMGvZDInv0uRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=dddfd252\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180522%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58224017&h=35ed8c5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180522&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58224017</a><br />\n【車股有難？】中國大削汽車及零部件進口關稅<br />\n<br />\n中國財政部公佈，自今年7月1日起，將降低汽車整車及零部件進口關稅。汽車整車稅率為25%及20%的，將降至15%。新政策已經國務院批准。<br />\n<br />\n公告指，為進一步擴大改革開放，推動供給側結構性改革，促進汽車產業升級轉型，滿足人民群眾消費需求，今年7月1日起，汽車整車稅率為25%的135個稅號，及稅率為20%的4個稅號的稅率將降至15%。<br />\n<br />\n另外，汽車零部件稅率分別為8%、10%、15%、20%、25%的共79個稅號的稅率將降至6%。<br />\n<br />\n財政部表示，中國維護多邊貿易體制，是次降低汽車進口關稅是中國進一步擴大改革開放的重大措施。降稅後，中國汽車整車平均稅率13.8%，零部件平均稅率6%。<br />\n<br />\n寶馬稱，對中國下調汽車進口關稅的公告表示歡迎，在進行價格評估後將作出積極回應。較早前，保時捷稱已開始評估中國汽車關稅新政，將宣佈調價措施。"},{"pid":"5a880e81754b1c15fbb6476df8ef511342a30fc7","tid":673965,"uid":104699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T09:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af101ac65b096524a99d26729e2541ca8ae40f5f","tid":673965,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T09:52:41.000Z","msg":"嘩 釋出善意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/do